{"name":"Anne the Little Chatterer","type":"npc","flags":{"btActorType":"villager","btNpcSubtype":"minor","btCustomOL":"5"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"npcType":"villager","attributes":{"soma":{"max":0,"current":0},"wounds":{"max":1,"current":0,"extra":{"value":0,"max":1}},"xp":0},"background":"","descriptors":["Lady Elizaveta has instructed me to keep her informed about what is being said in town. I do my job as a spy because I don’t want her to stop giving me gifts."],"agenda":"Spy on the townsfolk for Lady Elizaveta in exchange for gifts.","gifts":[],"darkEgo":{"trigger":"","gift":""},"weapons":[],"objects":[],"conditions":[],"notes":""},"_id":"4d83e021b273cb40"}
{"name":"Corinne the Housekeeper","type":"npc","flags":{"btActorType":"villager","btNpcSubtype":"minor","btCustomOL":"3"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"npcType":"villager","attributes":{"soma":{"max":0,"current":0},"wounds":{"max":1,"current":0,"extra":{"value":0,"max":1}},"xp":0},"background":"","descriptors":["I know all rumors in the village, partly because I start most of them myself. I’m easily offended and I love receiving gifts."],"agenda":"Spread rumors and collect gossip, especially when she’s given something in return.","gifts":[],"darkEgo":{"trigger":"","gift":""},"weapons":[],"objects":[],"conditions":[],"notes":""},"_id":"7349e65079c42b90"}
{"name":"Didier the Grumpy Old Man","type":"npc","flags":{"btActorType":"villager","btNpcSubtype":"minor","btCustomOL":"5"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"npcType":"villager","attributes":{"soma":{"max":0,"current":0},"wounds":{"max":1,"current":0,"extra":{"value":0,"max":1}},"xp":0},"background":"","descriptors":["I hate all foreigners and I miss the old baron. He knew how to stand up for himself. Not like that lax Gerard who even married a foreigner!"],"agenda":"Criticize the current leadership and stir up resentment in the village.","gifts":[],"darkEgo":{"trigger":"","gift":""},"weapons":[],"objects":[],"conditions":[],"notes":""},"_id":"a0766b6d7b5474ac"}
{"name":"Genevieve the Chemist","type":"npc","flags":{"btActorType":"villager","btNpcSubtype":"minor","btCustomOL":"3"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"npcType":"villager","attributes":{"soma":{"max":0,"current":0},"wounds":{"max":1,"current":0,"extra":{"value":0,"max":1}},"xp":0},"background":"","descriptors":["I escaped from a past full of witchcraft and deceit. I know how to summon spirits and talk with them."],"agenda":"Avoid being exposed for her past and stay useful to the village through her chemistry.","gifts":[],"darkEgo":{"trigger":"","gift":""},"weapons":[],"objects":[],"conditions":[],"notes":""},"_id":"80d364d440d56f7e"}
{"name":"Marcel the Time-Waster","type":"npc","flags":{"btActorType":"villager","btNpcSubtype":"minor","btCustomOL":"3"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"npcType":"villager","attributes":{"soma":{"max":0,"current":0},"wounds":{"max":1,"current":0,"extra":{"value":0,"max":1}},"xp":0},"background":"","descriptors":["I frequently wander the town and may be found anywhere. Once, I saw a young girl at the Oak Glade, but no one believed my story because I am too young."],"agenda":"Be heard and prove that what he saw in the Oak Glade is real.","gifts":[],"darkEgo":{"trigger":"","gift":""},"weapons":[],"objects":[],"conditions":[],"notes":""},"_id":"088c222bd97cf07d"}
{"name":"Nicholas the Huntsman","type":"npc","flags":{"btActorType":"villager","btNpcSubtype":"minor","btCustomOL":"5"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"npcType":"villager","attributes":{"soma":{"max":0,"current":0},"wounds":{"max":1,"current":0,"extra":{"value":0,"max":1}},"xp":0},"background":"","descriptors":["I know the ferocity of wolves and I can’t wait to show off in front of Baron Gerard."],"agenda":"Earn recognition from Baron Gerard by proving himself useful in the hunt.","gifts":[],"darkEgo":{"trigger":"","gift":""},"weapons":[],"objects":[],"conditions":[],"notes":""},"_id":"1b70a1b7cefa30ca"}
{"name":"Guards of Gerard Dubois","type":"npc","flags":{"btActorType":"villager","btNpcSubtype":"minor","btCustomOL":"5"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"attributes":{"soma":{"max":0,"current":0},"wounds":{"max":1,"current":0,"extra":{"value":0,"max":1}},"xp":0},"background":"","descriptors":["We are duty-bound — as long as we get paid."],"agenda":"Vincent is the boss. We’ll follow his lead.","gifts":[],"darkEgo":{"trigger":"","gift":""},"weapons":[],"objects":[],"conditions":[],"notes":""},"_id":"32b620c8d201e8d9"}